{"tid":2414032,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曝超狂穿搭！Lisa「內衣外穿」性感回歸　台上解放美尻","createTime":"2021-02-19T06:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T09:42:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cd39235c61814f380f68db6bcfe9c602e39572a1","tid":2414032,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"南韓超人氣女團BLACKPINK的成員Lisa再度回歸大陸綜藝選秀節目《青春有你3》擔任舞蹈導師，已經是CELINE的代言人，不僅IG中滿滿都是CELINE的時尚穿搭照，就連上節目也不放過，將CELINE 2021春夏內衣外穿，火辣S曲線，美到讓網友們「全跪下了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3031539-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3031539-PH.jpg&h=dfd1d3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa受邀擔任中國選秀節目《青春有你3》舞蹈導師。（圖／翻攝自lalalalisa_m微博）<br />\n<br />\n日前Lisa在微博PO出了參加節目錄影的照片，其中一套全白造型，以白色襯衫搭配白色超短緊身裙，最厲害的是，她在襯衫外搭配了一件CELINE 2021春夏內衣，以內衣外穿方式搭出層次，讓網友驚呼：「太會穿了吧！」、「這招太絕、太高級了」、「應該只有Lisa能駕馭吧！」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3031538-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3031538-PH.jpg&h=1e5f0c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa受邀擔任中國選秀節目《青春有你3》舞蹈導師。（圖／翻攝自lalalalisa_m微博）<br />\n<br />\n不僅上身穿得超時尚，連下半身也不放過，Lisa的腳上踩著黑色及膝長靴，完全襯出了她的逆天長腿，照片中一個華麗轉身，A4腰、蜜桃臀，性感曲線盡現，辣到還衝上微博熱搜。Lisa完全靠著絕美外表與超高人氣，甫出道就晉升時尚寵兒，手握CELINE、BVLGARI以及mac等大牌代言，不久前還公布成為ANDAM awards法國時尚藝術大獎評審之一，僅僅23歲就有如此狂的經歷，也讓粉絲們好佩服！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3031536-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3031536-PH.jpg&h=4c292779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa為M.A.C彩妝代言人。（圖／翻攝自lalalalisa_m微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/19/3031537-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2F3031537-PH.jpg&h=8da7f8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa連日常穿搭都是CELINE。（圖／翻攝自lalalalisa_m微博）"},{"pid":"67bfb7adb829ad982840a4510747f60afc2a6260","tid":2414032,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"秦國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341741352e5516bd8d3e4c52f4fbe4f70a322a85","tid":2414032,"uid":239912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"我以為係香港Lisa..."},{"pid":"913d272a32532f2ddc6ace36860ad7f6e79f0a67","tid":2414032,"uid":320858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"內衣又冇、又唔係回歸、尻在哪？"},{"pid":"045dd447d218878f5ef4cbc78c6ba482c462fffb","tid":2414032,"uid":162539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔係另一個lisa...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7ade2fc0a2b284dbe1e52569fe5eaf8a80ce6e","tid":2414032,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"045dd447d218878f5ef4cbc78c6ba482c462fffb","tid":2414032,"uid":162539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔係另一個lisa...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"果個上左神台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28ba6f4de18024b680c5fb4134606542693c6ce","tid":2414032,"uid":1039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GSGOUf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GSGOUf.jpg&h=d25c9d3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48f1f04778f5ebce03cd515f32a61dc8c9ce176b","tid":2414032,"uid":78188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"哪有美尻⋯⋯個屎忽平過對波⋯⋯"},{"pid":"cdc26ee399ce6ca443605ecc128d43e9b7cb7b14","tid":2414032,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":